====== Data Schema ======

User
  String: _:user:nextid
  Hash: user:[id] {id, username, password, email, created_at, logged_at, has_avatar}
  String: user:username:[username] [id]
  String: user:email:[email] [id]
  Sorted Set: user:[id]:topics [topic_id] [topic_id]
  Sorted Set: user:[id]:replies [reply_id] [reply_id]

Topic
  String: _:topic:nextid
  Hash: topic:[id] {id, author_id, title, body, created_at}
  Set: topic:[id]:tags [tag]
  Sorted Set: topic:[id]:replies [reply_id] [reply_id]
  String: topic:[id]:num_of_replies [number of replies]

Reply
  String: _:reply:nextid
  Hash: reply:[id] {id, topic_id, author_id, entry, created_at}
  Sorted Set: topic:[id]:replies [id] [id]

Tag
  Sorted Set: tags [tag] [number of uses]
  Sorted Set: tag:[tag] [topic_id] [topic_id]


====== Web Structure ======

/
/signin
/signout
/signup
/user
/user/[username]
/user/settings
/user/settings/profile
/topic
/topic/[topic id]
/tag
/tag/[tag]

